Hey,

As I mentioned previously, you can create a custom implementation of
UriPrecedencePolicy to implement your desired crawl order. You can see how
the precedence value you generate is used in
BdbMultipleWorkQueues.calculateInsertKey(CrawlURI). Notably, the precedence
value only accounts for one byte of the insert key, so you&#39;re limited to
255 precedence levels. There is room for finer customization, but that
would involve custom implementations of other classes in addition to
UriPrecedencePolicy.

But this
might be more
 advanced usage than you&#39;
re
 comfortable with
, especially if you didn&#39;t understand my previous emails. 
I&#39;m still not sure what you&#39;re trying to do, exactly. You say &quot;crawl
sequence/ order with Ascending, Descending or Random&quot;, but what are you
sorting by? Alphabetically by url??

Noah


